1 0 0 1 50 728 Tm (## Run and Test) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 714 Tm (- Run tests:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 700 Tm (  PYTHONPATH=src python -m pytest -q) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 686 Tm (- Start bot:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 672 Tm (  python -m kipsoiwet_bot) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 658 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 644 Tm (## Telegram Commands) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 630 Tm (- /start) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 616 Tm (- /status) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 602 Tm (- /next) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 588 Tm (- /won) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 574 Tm (- /lost) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 560 Tm (- /reset) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 546 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 532 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 518 Tm (## Predetermined Full-Day Sequence Mode) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 504 Tm (- Prepare `SEQUENCE_FILE` with ordered outcomes \(`UP`/`DOWN`\) from the first trade onward. It) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 490 Tm (can be one day or multi-week/month length.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 476 Tm (- Add to `.env`: `SEQUENCE_FILE=./data/day_sequence.txt`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 462 Tm (- In Telegram use:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 448 Tm (  - `/daystatus` to view current slot and remaining outcomes) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 434 Tm (  - `/advance win` or `/advance loss` to settle the next candle according to the predetermined) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 420 Tm (sequence) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 406 Tm (- The first trade is always forced to `UP` when sequence mode starts.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 392 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 378 Tm (## Notes) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 364 Tm (- Keep DRY_RUN=true initially.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 350 Tm (- If market snapshot arrives after BET_WINDOW_SECONDS, skip candle.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 336 Tm (- Add risk controls before live execution: max drawdown, max streak, cooldown.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 322 Tm (- No maximum stake cap is enforced by default in this version.) Tj
